Name: Update an existing booking
Description: This test ensures that an existing booking can be updated using PUT /booking/{id}.

Name: Create a new booking
Description: This test verifies the ability to create a new booking using the POST /booking endpoint.

Name: Retrieve booking by ID
Description: This test checks whether a booking can be retrieved by its ID using GET /booking/{id}.

Name: Delete a booking
Description: This test confirms that a booking can be deleted and that it returns 404 after deletion.
